      "baseline": 17,
      "autoResize": false,
      "text": "Problem\n- Build a recipe intelligence PoC\n- Task 1 is required\n- Task 2 is optional\n\nData\n- About 68k recipes in JSON\n- Ingredients are free text\n- Quantity and units add noise",
      "originalText": "Problem\n- Build a recipe intelligence PoC\n- Task 1 is required\n- Task 2 is optional\n\nData\n- About 68k recipes in JSON\n- Ingredients are free text\n- Quantity and units add noise"
