      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 17,
      "autoResize": false,
      "text": "Functional\n- Ingest recipes into queryable\nstorage\n- Return top 10 cooccurrence\nresults\n- Return top 5 duplicates for\nTask 2\n\nNon-functional\n- Keep PoC simple\n- Be deterministic and testable\n- Keep ingest and queries fast",
      "originalText": "Functional\n- Ingest recipes into queryable storage\n- Return top 10 cooccurrence results\n- Return top 5 duplicates for Task 2\n\nNon-functional\n- Keep PoC simple\n- Be deterministic and testable\n- Keep ingest and queries fast"
    },
