      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 17,
      "autoResize": false,
      "text": "Layers\n- Handlers: HTTP and CLI contracts\n- Services: orchestration and business rules\n- Repository: SQL and persistence\n- Domains and schemas: typed models\n\nWhy\n- Simple DI through __init__\n- Small and backend-friendly PoC",
      "originalText": "Layers\n- Handlers: HTTP and CLI contracts\n- Services: orchestration and business rules\n- Repository: SQL and persistence\n- Domains and schemas: typed models\n\nWhy\n- Simple DI through __init__\n- Small and backend-friendly PoC"
    },
