      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Core\n• settings, exceptions\n\nServices\n• ingest, normalization, cooccurrence, duplicates\n\nRepository\n• SQLiteRepository + SQL queries\n\nDomains / Handlers\n• typed models + CLI / FastAPI",
      "originalText": "Core\n• settings, exceptions\n\nServices\n• ingest, normalization, cooccurrence, duplicates\n\nRepository\n• SQLiteRepository + SQL queries\n\nDomains / Handlers\n• typed models + CLI / FastAPI"
    },
    {
      "id": "JBNU4zwbNQiBEpzKMG74p",
