      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Tradeoffs & deployment",
      "originalText": "Tradeoffs & deployment"
    },
    {
      "id": "6FKHySvyR3GLmGd0kaEML",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1216.8553429687793,
      "y": 535.3503480638253,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2013700222,
      "version": 145,
      "versionNonce": 603572514,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696357167,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b0R",
      "width": 833.1993408203125,
      "height": 175,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Tradeoffs\nSQLite keeps the PoC simple and fast enough\nNormalization is deterministic, not ML-driven\nTF-IDF is explainable but not perfect\n\nDeployment\nDockerfile supports dev and prod\nCompose provides api, ingest, and test services",
      "originalText": "Tradeoffs\nSQLite keeps the PoC simple and fast enough\nNormalization is deterministic, not ML-driven\nTF-IDF is explainable but not perfect\n\nDeployment\nDockerfile supports dev and prod\nCompose provides api, ingest, and test services"
    },
