      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Recipe Intelligence API - Essential Architecture",
      "originalText": "Recipe Intelligence API - Essential Architecture"
    },
    {
      "id": "dETr2XH6It74D5UdlTrHf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1138.725143034668,
      "y": -1434.2853386910424,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 74800190,
      "version": 162,
      "versionNonce": 452945022,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1d",
      "width": 210.50389099121094,
      "height": 35,
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Problem & data",
      "originalText": "Problem & data"
    },
    {
      "id": "EMQv8DPv_gwMo__RHB7yC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1218.8773064250402,
      "y": -1382.880365568628,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 674964606,
      "version": 481,
      "versionNonce": 578136674,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1e",
      "width": 477.899658203125,
      "height": 300,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Goal\n• Build a recipe intelligence PoC\n• Task 1 required, Task 2 optional\n\nInputs\n• Allrecipes JSON dataset (~68k recipes)\n• Free-text ingredient strings\n\nKey issues\n• Quantity and units add noise\n• Same ingredient appears in many forms\n• Cooccurrence must count per recipe",
      "originalText": "Goal\n• Build a recipe intelligence PoC\n• Task 1 required, Task 2 optional\n\nInputs\n• Allrecipes JSON dataset (~68k recipes)\n• Free-text ingredient strings\n\nKey issues\n• Quantity and units add noise\n• Same ingredient appears in many forms\n• Cooccurrence must count per recipe"
    },
    {
      "id": "-kJv6UW1mgriUCtHljQWh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1151.72165396374,
      "y": -1031.0010307305847,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 413000894,
      "version": 309,
      "versionNonce": 685384894,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1f",
      "width": 318.47186279296875,
      "height": 35,
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Functional requirements",
      "originalText": "Functional requirements"
    },
    {
      "id": "4rtLspLFx7RBHwFx2LTW1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1217.5457288170267,
      "y": -961.0809985270976,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 658414846,
      "version": 310,
      "versionNonce": 81137186,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1g",
      "width": 403.2197570800781,
      "height": 125,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "• Ingest recipe JSON into queryable storage\n• Return top 10 ingredient cooccurrence results\n• Expose the assignment API contract\n• Optionally return top 5 duplicate recipes\n• Handle noisy ingredient text safely",
      "originalText": "• Ingest recipe JSON into queryable storage\n• Return top 10 ingredient cooccurrence results\n• Expose the assignment API contract\n• Optionally return top 5 duplicate recipes\n• Handle noisy ingredient text safely"
    },
    {
      "id": "gBnZN84JJXlMjd6BRhYTb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1154.2179931054181,
      "y": -779.4726131342377,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1235111230,
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 1710415102,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1h",
      "width": 327.9918212890625,
      "height": 35,
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Non-functional decisions",
      "originalText": "Non-functional decisions"
    },
    {
      "id": "nQn5YShK2vAkbpXQcUdcD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1222.862464310488,
      "y": -710.7070387181875,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 488502654,
      "version": 348,
      "versionNonce": 1291057634,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774696547681,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "b1i",
      "width": 374.73974609375,
      "height": 225,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Targets\n• Simple PoC with fast local setup\n• Deterministic ingest and query behavior\n\nDesign choices\n• SQLite for storage and aggregation\n• Bulk insert + SQL precomputation\n• FastAPI + Pydantic\n• Constructor injection for simple DI\n• Pytest coverage for both tasks",
      "originalText": "Targets\n• Simple PoC with fast local setup\n• Deterministic ingest and query behavior\n\nDesign choices\n• SQLite for storage and aggregation\n• Bulk insert + SQL precomputation\n• FastAPI + Pydantic\n• Constructor injection for simple DI\n• Pytest coverage for both tasks"
    },
